<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewr gnade
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Haller und <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>Ebn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> wal <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <add>das
                                    <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie uns also wol <expan>cze
                                    wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> getan und wir</add>
<expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>des</add>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleizz. Und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> wissen, daz uns botschaft
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> herauf <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, wie
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Beheim, eynig
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> sülle und das süll
                                <expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als in diser
                            <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tage
                        czü Tyernaw; und wenn derselb tag vergee, so main
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r,</expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künig <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, mitsampt <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        frawen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> künigin herauf gen
                                <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und fürbas gen Oche cze cziehen.
                        Und wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
